<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f6f9; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .header h1 { color: #e74c3c; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
        .content { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .alert-box { background-color: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .stat-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        .stat-table th, .stat-table td { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; text-align: left; }
        .stat-table th { color: #666; font-weight: normal; width: 40%; }
        .stat-table td { font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>⚠️ Budget Exceeded Alert</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>This is an automated alert to let you know that your recent transaction has caused you to exceed your budget for <strong>{{ budgetName }}</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                You have overspent this budget by <strong style="color: #e74c3c;">{{ overspentBy }} TND</strong>!
            </div>

            <table class="stat-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>Budget Name:</th>
                    <td>{{ budgetName }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Allocated Amount:</th>
                    <td>{{ amount }} TND</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Current Total Spent:</th>
                    <td style="color: #e74c3c;">{{ spentAmount }} TND</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Most Recent Expense:</th>
                    <td>{{ lastExpense }} TND ({{ lastCategory }})</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Please review your budget dashboard to make any necessary adjustments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from your Finance Management App.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
